to use:
- first download all packages using the command:
  pip install numpy pandas matplotlib faiss-cpu scikit-learn tqdm torch goatools

Make sure to also have the splits folder with all the folds in your
working directory

to run:
  python final.py

if you do not have enough storage on your disk, it will crash
but will create a fold_metrics.csv file before that happens to 
write final prediction, threshold, and f1 scores


